answersResultList.title: True Libra.
answersResultList.resultContent: As a true Libra, you're all about balance, from how you move physically to how you arrange your life. Relationships are everything to you. Each friend is a potential BFF, and each time you fall in love, you're exactly where you're supposed to be. You create harmony by promoting fairness, and you're a good listener when somebody needs to talk. Since being everyone else's balance point can put you under a lot of pressure, it's important to take good care of yourself. Remember, you're not the glue holding everything together. You're just the poster child for a system in balance.

answersResultList.title: Mostly Libra.
answersResultList.resultContent: If there's a group project at work, a team activity in the park, a band that needs your musical skills, or a party in progress, you are so there. You love being around people, whatever they're doing - even if it's not especially wise, healthy, economical, or even legal. In that sense, you're not quite a true Libra. Generosity comes easily to you, and you're eager to buy people's affections instead of earning them (which wouldn't be hard). You're probably a little sensitive around this topic if anyone calls you on it. You just want harmony to prevail, whatever the price.

You're probably a little sensitive around this topic if anyone calls you on it. You just want harmony to prevail, whatever the price.
